  "title": "Conversations, Act Three: The Sith Walks In",
  "summary": "Just as Lynae weighs Johanna's offer of a new life, Darth Malign, Johanna's estranged brother Tyler Damion and the Empire's new Ambassador to the CDU, sweeps into the Sandbar with two guards and begins probing the room through the Force. The near-human Malif greets the table before recoiling at Malign's intrusive tricks, while Johanna coldly orders her brother to leave them be. Malign needles Lynae as a coward and a traitor for fleeing to Caspar with her prisoners, but the exiled doctor stands her ground, defending free will and condemning the Empire's reliance on fear. The surgeon Brandis Finian arrives to assess whether Lynae deserves his help, and Malign delivers a parting threat to torment her forever before President Mahon, flanked by his Presidential Guards, interposes himself to brand the Sith persona non grata.",
